            "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord Server!</h1><p>You can join our Discord server where we're growing a small, friendly community based around Salio!<br><br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/pzDaBB6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >https://discord.gg/pzDaBB6</a><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_03.png?t=1546797480\" ></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Salio is a minimalistic, but still a super hard platform game about getting a tiny fellow through numerous rooms filled with various obstacles.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_07.png?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Reflex, coordination are what is needed to finish this extremely difficult platformer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><br><br>Tough levels, interesting mechanics, tight controls, secrets to find about and many more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Story mode with over 100 levels</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Custom mode with your or other player's self-made levels (Steam Workshop support)</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Rewarding achievements</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Trading cards, badges, emoticons and profile backgrounds availible for draw</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Level Editor</h2><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_06.gif?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Create, edit and publish your or other player's custom levels using an user friendly level editor!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lua Modding Support</h2> <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_05.gif?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Modify and add new content into the game with the help of Lua and Salio Modding Documentation!",
            "about_the_game": "Salio is a minimalistic, but still a super hard platform game about getting a tiny fellow through numerous rooms filled with various obstacles.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_07.png?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Reflex, coordination are what is needed to finish this extremely difficult platformer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><br><br>Tough levels, interesting mechanics, tight controls, secrets to find about and many more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Story mode with over 100 levels</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Custom mode with your or other player's self-made levels (Steam Workshop support)</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Rewarding achievements</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Trading cards, badges, emoticons and profile backgrounds availible for draw</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Level Editor</h2><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_06.gif?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Create, edit and publish your or other player's custom levels using an user friendly level editor!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lua Modding Support</h2> <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/875810/extras/image_05.gif?t=1546797480\" ><br><br>Modify and add new content into the game with the help of Lua and Salio Modding Documentation!",
